    "body_html": "<div style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 640px;\">\n<p>Bonjour <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name\"/>,</p>\n<p>Sauf erreur de ma part, votre facture <strong><t t-out=\"object.name\"/></strong> d'un montant de <strong><t t-out=\"format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id)\"/></strong> est toujours en attente de règlement (échéance dépassée depuis le <t t-out=\"format_date(object.invoice_date_due)\"/>).</p>\n<p>Merci de procéder au règlement <strong>sous huitaine</strong>, ou de me revenir si un point bloque ou si vous avez besoin d'un échéancier.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;\">\n  <a t-att-href=\"object.get_portal_url()\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px;\">Régler maintenant</a>\n</p>\n<p>Cordialement,<br/>Service Comptabilité — MY.LAB</p>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.4; margin-top: 24px;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding-right: 12px; border-right: 2px solid #c5a467; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0924/1922/7982/files/Logo-rond-noir-sans-fond.png?v=1773170347\" alt=\"MY.LAB\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\" style=\"border-radius: 50%; display: block;\"/>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding-left: 12px; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 1px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a;\">Service Comptabilité</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: #c5a467; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">MY.LAB</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 2px 0; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #999;\">T</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:+33485693347\" style=\"color: #333; text-decoration: none;\">04 85 69 33 47</a></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 2px 0; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #999;\">E</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:contact@mylab-shop.com\" style=\"color: #333; text-decoration: none;\">contact@mylab-shop.com</a></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"color: #999;\">W</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mylab-shop.com\" style=\"color: #c5a467; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">mylab-shop.com</a></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 9px; color: #999;\">231 Avenue de la Voguette, 84300 Cavaillon — France</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding-top: 5px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; font-size: 9px; color: #c5a467; font-style: italic;\">SARL STARTEC — SIRET 499 500 668 00059 — TVA FR38499500668</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n</div>"
