  {
    "id": 18,
    "name": "Invoice: Sending",
    "email_from": "\"Service Comptabilité MY.LAB\" <yoann@mylab-shop.com>",
    "reply_to": "yoann@mylab-shop.com",
    "body_html": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">Bonjour <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name or ''\">Client</t>,<br/><br/>Veuillez trouver ci-joint votre facture MYLAB n°<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" t-out=\"object.name or ''\">FAC/2026/00001</span><t t-if=\"object.invoice_origin\"> (réf. <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" t-out=\"object.invoice_origin or ''\">S00001</span>)</t> d'un montant de <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" t-out=\"format_amount(object.amount_total, object.currency_id) or ''\">0,00 €</span> TTC.<br/><br/><t t-if=\"object.payment_state in ('paid', 'in_payment')\">✅ Cette facture a déjà été réglée. Merci pour votre paiement.</t><t t-else=\"\">Veuillez utiliser la communication suivante pour votre paiement : <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" t-out=\"object.payment_reference or ''\">FAC/2026/00001</span><t t-if=\"object.partner_bank_id\"> sur le compte <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" t-out=\"object.partner_bank_id.acc_number or ''\">FR76 ...</span></t>.</t><br/><br/>Pour toute question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.<br/><br/></p><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.4; margin-top: 24px;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding-right: 12px; border-right: 2px solid #c5a467; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0924/1922/7982/files/Logo-rond-noir-sans-fond.png?v=1773170347\" alt=\"MY.LAB\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\" style=\"border-radius: 50%; display: block;\"/>\n    </td>\n    <td style=\"padding-left: 12px; vertical-align: top;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 1px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a;\">Service Comptabilité</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: #c5a467; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">MY.LAB</p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0 0 2px 0